Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,（主題曲「温柔的忘却」）\N（PV幕后花絮）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,哇，好惊人，好惊人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,穿这样就只能在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经41岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一模一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的景色也很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.50,0:00:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我会被开除
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这么低还不能拍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.91,0:00:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧，走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就快到学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.83,0:00:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是春日在《忧郁》中\N走下来的场面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.08,0:01:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.08,0:01:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,终于到了真正的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,来到真正的北高
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.41,0:01:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮，也很整齐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,刚好是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是学校诶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.08,0:01:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,到了这种年纪\N难得有机会回到学校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.91,0:01:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,很有活力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是春日吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,春日到北高来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.16,0:01:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真有活力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,很热情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:02:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,受到热情粉丝的迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到居然会被北高学生这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,拼命挥着手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,居然被北高学生这么说\N而且还是超级激动的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,（第一天  拍摄封面）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微走一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好，开始走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,再偏向侧面一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,侧面\N对对对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,身体向前，只有脸偏过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对...然后....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,来了来了，（雨）开始下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,开始下了哦\N为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,开始下了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,白天就开始下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是要怎么造假？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真的，真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？\N真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要跌倒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,明明天气这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微飘了一点\N真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真让人感动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,很感动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此，那就没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微过来一点...\N对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:05:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,侧面也不太对，变成...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,变成这样子了吧\N那边应该更凹凸一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,朝着港口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,再稍微...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,接着朝地面看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,可以把脚张开一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,往这边张开比较好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这边可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有车要过来了，有车来了\NOK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,会冷吗？不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,1 2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,OK，这里OK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好帅气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,再稍微...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要拍了，1 2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可以抬高一点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,请再抬高一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,先这样拍拍看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,1 2 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,请再抬高一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,再抬高点看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,抬高了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,抬高了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,1 2 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,试试看这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,1 2 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:07:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,1 2 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,脚交叉起来感觉就不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,1 2 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要拍吗？这边有一瓶茶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,1 2 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,（摄影顺利结束，因为好奇）\N（前往长门住的公寓看看）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我会误会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,都有安排好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害\N像是阿虚的家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,还有其实也有春日的家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是用这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,到处探访
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,长门住的公寓就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，没办法进去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因为平时有人住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都有来过对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有来过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,把帽沿拉高一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,大家早，我是白石稔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在来到《凉宫春日的消失》\N这部电影的主题曲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,由茅原实里演唱的《温柔的忘却》\N宣传影片的拍摄现场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才后面有出现怪怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,请大家不要太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只是想抢镜头而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我第一次看人家拍宣传影片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,很好奇会是什么感觉\N接下来就来看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,或许会拍到某些多余的人\N大家真的不要太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只是想抢镜头而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那么就请大家一起来欣赏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就去探访
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那种感觉可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他是制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,音乐制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这种感觉吗？\N已经在拍了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛太近了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这位是超厉害的制作人，斋藤滋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪的三人组
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,凉宮春日的消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,顺带一提
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,今天气温是多少度？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,今天气温是多少度？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,最低气温，零下1度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,最低气温，零下1度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,最高气温，4度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,4度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是山上超冷的\N其实...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她穿的那么少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然实里穿得那么少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,其实超级冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,很冷\N的确很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,其实现在我已经很佩服她了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,其实今天是我第一次听这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是，我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊\N没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,很期待，很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好像开始试拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,本来看不太出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真正开始拍之后\N整个气氛就不一样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,透过画面看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,表情完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该看过很多次了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,实里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都在叫实里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,白石也在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人叫白石...\N没有没有...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有人会叫我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,下次派人去大声叫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧，这个人是白石！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,超糟糕的...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.16,0:12:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那种我绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,白石也在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,大家请看，大家请看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多女高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,很受欢迎\N好惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我超喜欢你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,回应粉丝呼唤的超人气明星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样\N茅原小姐跟他们说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他们说白石也在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不要这样，算我求你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这个就饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,真的诶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,用宽银幕看就觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真的差很多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,因为稍微从下面拍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来很宽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有点圆弧的曲线感觉很...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,软化了僵硬感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是小孩子\N绝对无法从这个角度去看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这种高度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,居然说出这种哲学理论
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不是小孩子就无法看到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢让我们跟小孩子一样\N都能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀呀...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,（照明的滤镜似乎被风吹倒了）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀呀...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,原來也可以拍成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.16,0:14:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉好像电影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,后面变模糊的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,对，后面变模糊的话\N对对...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,斋藤先生，我也想接那种工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想接那种工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,白石用这个拍就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在后面找个背景拍就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好的...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下用这台摄影机\N从同样的角度帮你拍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是这个角度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好，卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好，OK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,笑容完全消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不，才没那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,才没那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧，伊藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我的眼睛说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是在演短剧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,才没那回事对吧，伊藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可以看着我的眼睛说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是拍上面，下面包起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,下面不会拍到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,今天全国都下大雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这里居然出太阳了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,居然出太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我是晴女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天丙丙出太阳，却下了雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,丙丙出太阳？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是明明出太阳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,的确下雪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,对 明明是个大晴天\N感觉超美的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,特写也很美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,做的夸张一点好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才只有一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,先看上面，再看回来？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,OK，谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不会冷吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你比起来，一点都不冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一点都不冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N还有他们两人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,三个人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,三位大美女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他说我们是三位大美女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,看到他们没反应\N以为是不想理我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,真的会很感动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,很多地方都跟动画一样\N对...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,跟动画一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一路走来...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,拍起来很有趣\N很感动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然很累
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,听说你的体力很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我听别人说你的体力很好\N我？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:18:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,的确体力很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,伊藤先生，今天感觉如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,今天感觉没有昨天冷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没有昨天冷？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不过体力比昨天差
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,结果还是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也出太阳，真的太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,本来说降雨概率是80%\N因为我是晴女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？\N今天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.75,0:19:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧\N就是啊，很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,伊藤先生也是个晴男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是个晴男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊\N他是角川书店的终极武器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不论去哪里都会出太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都觉得带我出外景很方便\N不用带伞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,（即使这两个晴男晴女同时都在）\N（看来降水概率也不低）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是终极武器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,开始了\N好，那就麻烦一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,准备，开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好，卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好，卡\N谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:19:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,风变冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,接着拍脚边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,应该不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,OK\N卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧，不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的吊臂状况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那叫超级吊臂\N特征是平行四边形
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是平行四边形\N在那里操作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,制造稳定效果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此\N好清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的好清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好，卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,效率挺高的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，今天如果不拍快一点\N会拍不完的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟在校内能用的时间有限
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不会冷吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.91,0:21:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,当然冷了，不过...\N说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不过...不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,开始拍之后就不会去想那些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,要拍了，预备
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:21:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好，卡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,卡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,可以再来一次吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.83,0:22:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.58,0:22:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好，卡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.41,0:22:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,卡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.50,0:22:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, OK\N那就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,（一旦开始拍 表情就改变）\N（集中于演技上）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,开始拍摄后...大约...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.00,0:22:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,经过了5个小时，还在继续拍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.33,0:22:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,实里也完全没休息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.50,0:23:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,持续在拍摄PV
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就同行来说，真的很敬佩她
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.08,0:23:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好，那开始吧\N开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.91,0:23:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,有车要来了\N请靠进来一点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.75,0:23:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,（日落后，开始今天最后的拍摄）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,（这个装置是\N这次拍摄的秘密武器）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.99,0:23:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.58,0:23:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,下的很密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.33,0:23:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是雪耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.33,0:23:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,（居然是人工降雪机）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.00,0:23:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,（实际上并非真正的雪）\N（而是飘下宛如泡泡的东西）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.33,0:23:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,掉在脸上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.00,0:23:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,看这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,看这边了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.41,0:24:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就尽量...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.50,0:24:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.75,0:24:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.66,0:24:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,太近了\N就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.08,0:24:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.25,0:24:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.83,0:24:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,現在稍微调少了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.66,0:24:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好...大概就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.91,0:24:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,想让雪下的温柔一点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.91,0:24:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那么最后一场戏，好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.66,0:24:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.16,0:24:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真的像是在下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.66,0:24:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,以上就是电影\N《凉宮春日的消失》主题曲
